About the Business

Business owner information

Shahil P.

Business Owner

We are giving traditional pizza kitchens a spin! We offer a variety of Indian infused pies, along with traditional Italian pizzas. Mouth-watering Indian appetizers, Mediterranean platters to name off the big hitters. And did we mention mocktails & freshly baked desserts to satisfy that ever demanding sweet tooth, we have it! Come with friends & family and enjoy San Francisco the Kinara way.

We had gol guppay/pani puri, fire fries, samosa chaat, chicken 69 bites, tandoori fish, chicken tikka masala, karhai chicken, curry pizza, tikka dum biryani, naan, and chai. Everything was super delicious and that's coming from someone super picky. I didn't care much for their samosa chaat or karahi chicken but all of the other items we tried were just perfect! InshaAllah will be coming back!

  • Swati P.
    San Francisco, CA
    95

    9/11/2020

    I stopped into Kinara to pick up some takeout for some friends and me. They were having a little photoshoot for some plated food, and the plating looked terrific! It made me wish I had visited before COVID. Everyone was wearing masks, including the chefs inside. This made me feel safe about ordering takeout from the restaurant.

    We got the Paneer Pathaka pizza, Chicken 69, and the Cauliflower Manchurian. Everything was delicious! The Paneer pizza was pretty big in comparison to some of the other Indian pizzas I've eaten. The appetizers were also cooked well and perfectly spicy for our taste. Sometimes Cauliflower Manchurian can lack flavor when it's not drenched in a sauce, but it was an excellent balance of flavor and still having that Manchurian bite. We all thoroughly enjoyed our dinner, and everyone was on the same page about going back!

    I will definitely be revisiting Kinara and am excited to try more items on the menu!

I always love to get the tikka dum biryani, pani puri shots, fire fries, green lantern chicken and chai! It never disappoints and comes packed with flavor. I enjoy spicy food so this hits the right spot so definitely anticipate that in their items.
    Both indoor and outdoor dining were options for us and it was nice to be in a location that was so well kept and clean. Can't recommend this place enough, it's a must try!
